TopicTitle: Jeb's Spaceship [Parody of Great Big Sea's Lukey]

Articles.Content:
This is something I made up on the bus from work, it\'s really silly but if you guys like it I\'ll put in the effort to record it this weekend.

To the tune Great Big Sea\'s Lukey:

A-ha, Kerbals it\'s-rocket-launch-day!

Well oh, Jeb\'s Spaceship has just one stage,

Ha, Kerbals!

Jeb\'s Spaceship has just one stage,

Kerbelest ship that you\'ve ever seen,

A-ha, Kerbals it\'s-rocket-launch-day!

A-ha, Kerbals it\'s-rocket-launch-day!

Well oh, Jeb\'s Blueprint has got no fine studies,

Ha, Kerbals!

Jeb\'s Blueprint has got no fine studies,

And every joint is held with strutting,

A-ha, Kerbals it\'s-rocket-launch-day!

A-ha, Kerbals it\'s-rocket-launch-day!

Well I says 'Jeb, now that won\'t leave ground'

Ha, Kerbals!

I says 'Jeb, now that won\'t leave ground'

'It\'s got boosters so it is sound'

A-ha, Kerbals it\'s-rocket-launch-day!

A-ha, Kerbals it\'s-rocket-launch-day!

Well I says Jeb 'See, I don\'t care'

Ha, Kerbals!

I says Jeb 'See, I don\'t care'

'It\'ll get me to orbit of the Mun sipping Beer'

A-ha, Kerbals it\'s-rocket-launch-day!

A-ha, Kerbals it\'s-rocket-launch-day!

Oh, Jeb\'s has brought back payload,

Ha, Kerbals!

Oh, Jeb\'s has brought back payload,

One Mun rock for a thousand fuel,

A-ha, Kerbals it\'s-rocket-launch-day!

A-ha, Kerbals it\'s-rocket-launch-day!

Well oh, Jeb\'s Spaceship has just one stage,

Ha, Kerbals!

Jeb\'s Spaceship has just one stage,

Kerbelest ship that you\'ve ever seen,

A-ha, Kerbals it\'s-rocket-launch-day!

A-ha, Kerbals it\'s-rocket-launch-day!

A-ha, Kerbals it\'s-rocket-launch-day!
Hey that\'s good! I usually enjoy parody lyrics anyway, but this is hokey dokey!
